# Deny the LangGraph build context by default.  `source.root = "."` makes the
# CLI enumerate otherwise-unignored workspace entries into explicit Dockerfile
# ADD instructions, so a denylist can silently bake editor state, checkpoints,
# generated output, or a newly-created secret into an application image.
**

# The Python distribution and generated LangGraph image recipe need only this
# locked package metadata and the package source.  Keep directory and contents
# as separate exceptions so Docker can traverse the otherwise-ignored parent.
!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!uv.lock
!langgraph.json
!src/
!src/**
